        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "CHAPTER twenty one-THEY BICKER ABOUT THE FORD",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66277_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66277/7197_66277_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "Said the lad, \"I am Ali, the son of Grey, and the Hall Sun hath sent me to thee with this word: 'Are ye coming?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66277_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66277/7197_66277_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "Said Otter, \"Art thou going back to Wolfstead, son?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66277_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66277/7197_66277_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "\"Yea, at once, my father,\" said Ali.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66277_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66277/7197_66277_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "Hast thou all this in thine head?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66277_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66277/7197_66277_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "Then go thy ways.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66277_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66277/7197_66277_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "So did they, and there was little delay, for men were sleeping with one eye open, as folk say, and many were already astir.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66277_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66277/7197_66277_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "So in a little while they were all in the saddle, and the mist yet stretched low over the meadow; for the morning was cool and without wind.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66277_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66277/7197_66277_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "And on the other hand it was high noon by now, so that he had given respite to the stay at homes of the Wolfings, so that they might get them into the wood.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66277_000019_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66277/7197_66277_000019_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "But the romans crossed the ford in good earnest and were soon all gathered together on the western bank making them ready for the march to Wolfstead.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66277_000019_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66277/7197_66277_000019_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "Therefore he had no fear of their escaping him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "And these first were the riders of the Bearings, and the Wormings, (for they had out gone the others who were afoot).",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000002_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000002_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "So they rode back to where they had left their folk talking with them of Otter; and the Bearings were sitting grim upon their horses and somewhat scowling on Otter's men.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000002_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000002_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "Then the foremost of those who had come back from the houses waved his hand toward the ford, but could say nought for a while; but the captain and chief of the Bearings, a grizzled man very big of body, whose name was Arinbiorn, spake to that man and said; \"What aileth thee Sweinbiorn the Black?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "He said:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "Where were the bones of thy mother lying?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "Said Sweinbiorn:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "So rode they over the meadow and into the ford and over it, and Otter's company stood on the bank to meet them, and shouted to see them; but the others made but little noise as they crossed the water.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "So when they were on the western bank Arinbiorn came among them of Otter, and cried out: \"Where then is Otter, where is the War duke, is he alive or dead?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "What is this?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "Are we not now of more avail to you, O men of the Bearings, than our dead corpses would have been?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "Arinbiorn answered not, but his face waxed red, as if he were struggling with a weight hard to lift: then said Otter:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "Arinbiorn answered calmly: \"Maybe in a little hour from now, or somewhat more.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "Let the War duke rule here, as is but meet and right.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000023_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000023_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "Yet if I might speak and not break the peace of the Goths, then would I say this, that it might be better for us to fall on these romans at once before they have cast up a dike about them, as Fox telleth is their wont, and that even in an hour they may do much.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "\"Thorbiorn, thou art old, and shouldest not be void of prudence.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "\"What is this to do?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "And he was very wrath, and turned away; and again there was a murmur and a hum about him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "But while these had been speaking aloud, Sweinbiorn had been talking softly to some of the younger men, and now he shook his naked sword in the air and spake aloud and sang:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "Therewith he waved his sword over his head, and made as if he would spur onward.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "But Arinbiorn thrust through the press and outwent him and cried out:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "Then on he rode nor looked behind him, and the riders of the Bearings and the Wormings drew themselves out of the throng, and followed him, and rode clattering over the meadow towards Wolfstead.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "A few of the others rode with them, and yet but a few.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000032_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000032_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "Howbeit, man looked askance at man, as if in shame to be left behind.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "\"Now at last has come the time to die, and let them of the Markmen who live hereafter lay us in howe.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7197_66278_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7197/66278/7197_66278_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7197",
        "content": "Many men perceived that he sang, and saw that he was merry, howbeit few heard his very words, and yet all were glad of him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    }
]